text: Title: HR Policy (Internal) - Maternity leave: 26 weeks paid for eligible employees. - Apply via HR portal at least 30 days in advance where possible.

Title: On-call Incident Escalation Runbook (Internal) - Severity levels: SEV1 (critical), SEV2 (major), SEV3 (minor) - SEV1: page primary + secondary on-call immediately. - Escalate to Incident Commander within 10 minutes if impact persists. - Post-incident: write RCA within 48 hours.

Title: Logging & PII Policy (Internal) - Do not log full PAN, Aadhaar, passport numbers, or passwords. - Mask sensitive values: keep last 4 digits only when necessary. - For debugging, prefer request_id correlation over raw payload logging. - Access to logs must follow least privilege and be audited.
